quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  4,114,Lā Khayra Fī Kathīrin Min Najwāhum 'Illā Man 'Amara Bişadaqatin 'Aw Ma`rūfin 'Aw 'Işlāĥin Bayna An-Nāsi Wa Man Yaf`al Dhālika Abtighā'a Marđāati Allāhi Fasawfa Nu'utīhi 'Ajrāan `Ažīmāan
  4,115,Wa Man Yushāqiqi Ar-Rasūla Min Ba`di Mā Tabayyana Lahu Al-Hudá Wa Yattabi` Ghayra Sabīli Al-Mu'uminīna Nuwallihi Mā Tawallá Wa Nuşlihi Jahannama Wa Sā'at Maşīrāan
  4,116,Inna Allāha Lā Yaghfiru 'An Yushraka Bihi Wa Yaghfiru Mā Dūna Dhālika Liman Yashā'u Wa Man Yushrik Billāhi Faqad Đalla Đalālāan Ba`īdāan
  4,117,In Yad`ūna Min Dūnihi 'Illā 'Ināthāan Wa 'In Yad`ūna 'Illā Shayţānāan Marīdāan
  4,118,La`anahu Allāhu Wa Qāla La'attakhidhanna Min `Ibādika Naşībāan Mafrūđāan
  4,119,Wa La'uđillannahum Wa La'umanniyannahum Wa La'āmurannahum Falayubattikunna 'Ādhāna Al-'An`ām Wa La'āmurannahum Falayughayyirunna Khalqa Allāhi Wa Man Yattakhidhi Ash-Shayţāna Walīyāan Min Dūni Allāhi Faqad Khasira Khusrānāan Mubīnāan
  4,120,Ya`iduhum Wa Yumannīhim Wa Mā Ya`iduhumu Ash-Shayţānu 'Illā Ghurūrāan
  4,121,Ūlā'ika Ma'wāhum Jahannamu Wa Lā Yajidūna `Anhā Maĥīşāan